content.rendered:
Directed by Ali Abbas Zafar. Musa Muhammed Olayinka.

Written by Ali Abbas Zafar. Ali Abbas Zafar. Aditya Chopra. Writer Bhaiya. Ali Abbas Zafar.

Cast Salman Khan(Tiger / Avinash Singh Rathore). Katrina Kaif(Zoya). Paresh Rawal(Theuban / Firdaus). Anupriya Goenka(Poorna). Kumud Mishra(Rakesh). Kashmira Irani(Sana). Sajjad Delafrooz(Abu Usman). Anant Vidhaat Sharma(Karan). Girish Karnad(Shenoy). Neha Hinge(Nafisa). Nawab Shah(Pawan). Angad Bedi(Namit). Suraj Rana(Tiger’s Friend). Ryan Sturz(White Sam). Zachary Coffin(Garry). Ivan Rodrigues(India’s Ambassador to Iraq). Paresh Pahuja(Azaan Akbar). Vibhoutee Sharma(Jiya). Al Yasaha Naim(Naim). Sal Yusuf(Al Amir Bagdawi). Steve Lorrigan(Adam Kerry). Varun V. Sharma(M.E.A Officer). Satkeer(Satish). Gavie Chahal(Captain Abrar). Khalida Jan(Naghma). Katrina Ross(Self – Miri). Akdas Hayat(RAW Officer). Raj Karmakar(Tiger’s Friend).Hossein Rahmani Manesh. Gurii(Gurii). Kris Fade(Iraqi Father). Sharanya Menon(M.E.A Officer). Aamir Naik(Tiger’s Brother). Arafatur Rahman(Imran Khan). Najmeddin AlHadad(Hakim). Md. Jasim Uddin(Siddu (credit only)).Sujeet Kumar Sharma. Jineet Rath(Hassan). Shanti Lal Bhana(Tiger’s Friend). Prince Dutta(Tiger’s friend). Danish Bhatt(Captain Javed). Raaf Chaudhary(ISI Agent). Rohit KaduDeshmukh(Captain Gautam). 

Languages Hindi. English.

Producers Jamal Araissi. Aditya Chopra. Sudhanshu Kumar. Ishvinder Maddh. Hind Nabulsi. Andreas Payer. Bharat Rawail. Aashish Singh. Navmeet Singh.

Production SVO Special Vehicle Operation. Atlanta Productio. Yash Raj Film.
